General.Name: Pegroco Invest AB Pfd.
General.Description: Pegroco Invest AB (publ) is a private equity firm specializing in buyouts, acquisition, middle markets, and mature stage investments. It primarily focuses on unlisted companies, predominantly in Sweden. The firm seeks to invest in the energy and clean technology sector. It considers investments between SEK 1 million ($0.14 million) and SEK 10 million ($1.40 million) in companies having an enterprise value between SEK 10 million ($1.24 million) and SEK 500 million ($61.85 million). The firm invests in companies with a turnover between SEK 50 million ($7.02 million) and SEK 300 million ($42.11 million). The firm seeks minority or majority stakes. Pegroco Invest AB publ was founded in 2007 and is based in Göteborg, Sweden with an additional office in Stockholm, Sweden.
